						<summary>

						<p>This is damaged and dated <hi rend="bold">Chāḷukya-Vikrama year 33, Sarvadhāri, • • • • • • • Uttarāyaṇa-saṅkrānti</hi> probably corresponding to <hi rend="bold">A.D. 1107 December 24 Thursday,</hi> in the reign of the Chāḷukya king <hi rend="bold">Tribhuvanamalladēva.</hi> It records the grant of some land made by a <hi rend="italic">Daṇḍanāyaka</hi> (name lost) in charge of the tollrevenue, for the service of the god Vīrēśvaradēva.</p>						

